The variables 
   $user.dir
   $user.home
may be used and will be replaced to the current directory and
the users home directory respectively.

You may set $XMLBLASTER_HOME in your JVM environment or here, e.g.
   $XMLBLASTER_HOME=$user.home/xmlBlaster
and use it as a variable in this file.
